{"tid":298091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廿餘歲青年九龍塘碧華花園墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-06-26T04:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T07:45:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4004fa4179a6d14d19a6b8b73720dd554244b0","tid":298091,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170626/s00001/d9bb1ffebb7a604ab6cd057553f7f262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170626%2Fs00001%2Fd9bb1ffebb7a604ab6cd057553f7f262.jpg&h=53b4d20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘豪宅發生墮樓案。現場喇沙利道碧華花園8座，早上10時許，一名20餘歲青年由上址高處墮下，昏迷倒卧對開行車通道，送院不治，警方正調查事件。"},{"pid":"71dad366d5131a598fc6ae54c71b3e6691c6950b","tid":298091,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170626/s00001/d968a5efd7177a814154e6f5dbc71769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170626%2Fs00001%2Fd968a5efd7177a814154e6f5dbc71769.jpg&h=9de1fa2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清潔工人事後在事主倒卧位置進行清潔。（林智傑攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00001/1498449415022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00001%2F1498449415022&d=QXPzg7KFaPO1RB7uCK5ohozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cd1cb7c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00001%2F1498449415022&h=6f4e35d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00001/1498449415022</a>"},{"pid":"b5f0eb929e93b6e676369deae83dce5c646f7b82","tid":298091,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"早上10時11分，警方接報九龍塘喇沙利道碧華花園8座，一名20餘歲青年由高處墮下，倒卧屋苑內的行車通道。救護員趕至替事主急救後，將他送廣華醫院，惜告不治。警方登樓調查，死者家人這才知道他在睡房推開窗墮下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170626/large/1498449246_6dc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170626%2Flarge%2F1498449246_6dc7.jpg&h=83dc3ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者家人落樓了解情況時忍不住落淚。(簡明恩攝)"},{"pid":"5339205dd8fe22f9729e8f3295fcd8cab4b7b423","tid":298091,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd034abdd005807c5e9fc08929468eebc74e5c3","tid":298091,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"贏在起跑線都自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d433e0b5ee40f295f9c2f9f140e5898af1fe3369","tid":298091,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7df58edcd34ea89fb4f13ceb9bbb580b1928303","tid":298091,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"咁都要死，大家仲點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaad5f3b6e8f79710caf3302cb1b58b62e3c101","tid":298091,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa7aa01995ecd84bf8332cfa2f2fcc00c53a44b","tid":298091,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都要死，大家仲點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫啲窮撚情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf13771b89c40e9397574ec9e923e30c1a97b46","tid":298091,"uid":51436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201